<title>UK: Merrill Lynch sets warrants on Alusuisse-Lonza.</title>
<headline>Merrill Lynch sets warrants on Alusuisse-Lonza.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Merrill Lynch Capital Markets AG says it has issued a total of three million American-style call warrants, on Alusuisse-Lonza Holding Ltd.</p>
<p>20 warrants control one share.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    950.00 SFR		PREMIUM	7.65 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     3.65 SFR		  GEARING	13.05 X</p>
<p> EXERCISE PERIOD 10.SEP.96-21.MAR.97   PAYDATE	05.SEP.96</p>
<p> LISTING	   SWISS EXCHANGE	  MIN EXER LOT 100</p>
<p>SPOT REFERENCE  950.00 SFR</p>
<p> NOTES	     PRICES QUOTED ON REUTER PAGE  MLZE</p>
<p>-- Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
</text>
